          "date": "2022-07-27 15:15:06.000000000",
          "tz": -360
        },
        "subject": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Debugfs for transaction stats",
        "message": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Debugfs for transaction stats\n\nWhile tools such as LNet selftest can be used to infer kfilnd\ntransaction duration, it does not provide any insight into where in\nthe transaction time is spent. For each kfilnd LNet network\ninterface, four sets of transaction stats are recorded: average time,\nin nsecs, an initiator and target transaction is spent in each\ntransaction state with various LNet message lengths, and the average\ntime, in nsecs, an initiator and target transaction takes to\ncomplete with various LNet message lengths. In addition, a reset file\nis provide to reset all the stats.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-9378\nSigned-off-by: Ian Ziemba <ian.ziemba@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I36b29757c8c3c3372737e9dc2b69dec4cb252caa\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
